hing the government just couldn't allow.</p>\n<p>Fast forward to the modern day what &quot;law&quot; exists as a tax and that is the very nature by which it was allowed to become law? The Affordable Care Act i.e. &quot;Obamacare&quot;. Both laws were pushed and advocated under false pretenses. Therefore they were fraudulent at their core, and advanced as legislation for the sole purpose that the government could garner clandestine revenue.\nThis new revelation can be used as a wedge of legal precedent for the destruction of the ACA I can only pray some one sees it...</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 15, "score_up": 134, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZMK5Gim", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 75, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8551730, "raw_content": "", "author": "kek_saved_the_world", "created": 1775928393197, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Floppybutthole", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "media.scored.co", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZMK5Gim.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://media.scored.co/post/NTXQHKsMtD9M.jpeg", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [{"reference": "/scale/JVXQQBPQd36huXWv.png", "width": 576, "content-type": "png", "height": 768}], "blurhash": "UJMQt{xuIU?b~qt7ozNGRPaxs:Rj%MWBayRk", "full_resolution": [1437, 1077]}, "title": "If liberty means anything at all it means the right to tell people what they do not want to hear", "last_comment_created": 1775938289666, "content": "", "scor